### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/alim-inf
@contentType = application/json

### Get all AlimInfs
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get AlimInf by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Create new AlimInf
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "alimId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "babyId": 1,
  "todayId": 1,
  "name": "Test Name",
  "emotion": "Happy",
  "health": "Good",
  "nutrition": "Balanced",
  "activities": "Playing",
  "special": "First steps",
  "keywords": "milestone,development",
  "diary": "Today was a special day...",
  "date": "2024-03-20T10:00:00"
}

### Update AlimInf
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "alimId": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "babyId": 1,
  "todayId": 1,
  "name": "Updated Name",
